# ============================================================
# ZonWiki .gitignore
# 混合專案：筆記（Markdown/圖片）+ 後端（.NET 10）+ 前端（Next.js）
# 模式：blacklist（預設追蹤所有檔案，僅排除建置產物、密鑰、臨時檔）
# ============================================================

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# OS / 編輯器臨時檔
# ------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# IDE
# ------------------------------------------------------------
.vs/
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# .NET / C#
# ------------------------------------------------------------
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
x64/
x86/
*.pdb
*.cache
*.coverage
*.coveragexml
TestResults/
coverage/
.dotnet/
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json
msbuild.binlog

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# Node / Next.js
# ------------------------------------------------------------
node_modules/
.next/
out/
dist/
build/
.turbo/
.pnpm-store/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
.yarn/cache
.yarn/install-state.gz
next-env.d.ts

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# 密鑰 / 環境變數（絕對不要 commit）
# ------------------------------------------------------------
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
*.pfx
*.pem
*.key
secrets.json
appsettings.*.Local.json
appsettings.Production.json

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# Docker volumes / runtime
# ------------------------------------------------------------
.docker/
postgres-data/

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# Logs
# ------------------------------------------------------------
logs/
*.log

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# 備註
# ------------------------------------------------------------
# 筆記區/ 下的 .md 與圖片會被正常追蹤（無需顯式規則）
# 若未來要讓筆記區/raw 的私密草稿不被追蹤，可在 筆記區/raw/.gitignore 單獨設定
